    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284840/extras/d2d6ff4eec5712be436fccf2d031a931.poster.avif?t=1734448936\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284840/extras/d2d6ff4eec5712be436fccf2d031a931.webm?t=1734448936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284840/extras/d2d6ff4eec5712be436fccf2d031a931.mp4?t=1734448936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>您会处在无法通行的地带，行进困难，但能够做到。获得一辆 SUV，建造自己的宽敞车库；车库将容纳适合各种天气和路况的一批车辆。“穿越荒野”(Across the Wilds) 中的广阔荒野可以利用您在游戏过程中获得的技能来征服。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284840/extras/e99ce30d267aedae8bab2c0183e5bbd7.poster.avif?t=1734448936\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284840/extras/e99ce30d267aedae8bab2c0183e5bbd7.webm?t=1734448936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284840/extras/e99ce30d267aedae8bab2c0183e5bbd7.mp4?t=1734448936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>作为送货人，摆在您面前的任务并不轻松——要完好无损地将货物送到难以到达的目的地。最后的报酬取决于送货的情况。在特殊商店中购买装备，以此增加您的送货人能力。在汽车店里定制您的 SUV 来克服途中的各种障碍。按您的想法定制您的车辆，然后上路完成新的任务。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284840/extras/119de1d11df408d1e5f6ba162c55fe0f.poster.avif?t=1734448936\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284840/extras/119de1d11df408d1e5f6ba162c55fe0f.webm?t=1734448936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284840/extras/119de1d11df408d1e5f6ba162c55fe0f.mp4?t=1734448936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>独自开始您的旅程，或者召唤好友一起上路同行，互相帮助克服“穿越荒野”世界中的艰难困苦。<br><br><strong>特色： </strong><br>——有着各种野生动植物和优美风光的自然景观 <br>——您的主要对手是天气，它会让荒野中的生活变得错综复杂 <br>——按您的喜好随意定制送货人角色和居所 <br>——附各种履行条件的分派、合约、任务和挑战 <br>——无任何限制的开放世界，可在任意方向行走和驾驶，不会有任何人或物阻止您 <br>——每辆车有独特的调教，可让您将任务执行得更快、更好。经验丰富的送货人知道如何为特定的任务选择合适的车辆。<br><br>前进！",
